      • universalMode

        public static int universalMode
        When loading an XML or CSV, this mode will allow us to switch between selecting only universalbox labels or other labels. This is done by filtering the Order.AW field when parsing XML it can accept the following values LOAD_NON_UNIVERSAL_ONLY

        Ignore all universalbox labels and only collect non-universalbox labels e.g ProductLabel

        * LOAD_UNIVERSAL_ONLY

        Ignore all other labels and only collect universalbox labels

      • minAW

        public static int minAW
        During XML parsing, this value will dictate how many Order.AW fields we are willing to try to detect As our XML changes and more labels need to be printed for a single order, this value will need to be increased
